## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **1. Flask vs Streamlit**: Your detailed spec describes Flask + Jinja templates (which I recommend — it's more production-grade). But your 4-week image mentions "Streamlit" in Week 3 and 4. **Which do you prefer?** I'm proceeding with Flask as described in the detailed spec.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **2. Embedding Dimension**: Confirming: `all-MiniLM-L6-v2` → `vector(384)`. Your spec said `vector(1536)`. I'll use 384. OK?

> [!NOTE]
> **3. Trace Replay Backend**: The spec doesn't include a dedicated `/trace` API endpoint. I'll need to add `GET /analytics/trace/{query_id}` to return the full execution trace. I'll store trace data as a JSON column in `query_logs` (adding a `trace_data` column).

> [!NOTE]
> **4. Geolocation PK**: The geolocation CSV has no unique key. I'll add an auto-increment `id` as primary key and index on `geolocation_zip_code_prefix`.

