## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `pytest tests/unit/` — all unit tests pass
- `pytest tests/integration/` — full pipeline with mocked Groq + real PG
- `python tests/benchmark/benchmark_queries.py` — 20 queries, generate report

### Manual Verification
- Run `docker-compose up` and verify all 3 services start
- Test query interface with 5+ natural language questions
- Verify dashboard charts populate with real data
- Verify trace replay shows step-by-step execution
- Verify self-correction loop works (inject bad SQL, see retry)

### Browser Testing
- Use browser tool to navigate Flask frontend and verify all 3 pages render correctly
- Test query submission flow end-to-end
- Verify dark theme and responsive layout

