## Execution Approach

Per your instruction: **"Build one component at a time."**

I will start with **Week 1, Day 1-2** (Database + Schema Layer) and confirm it works before proceeding. The build order will be:

1. `docker-compose.yml` (PostgreSQL + pgvector)
2. `.env.example` + `backend/config.py`
3. `backend/db/connection.py` (asyncpg pool)
4. `backend/db/models.py` (DDL for all tables)
5. `backend/db/seed.py` (CSV import + embedding generation)
6. Test: verify all tables populated, run similarity search manually

Then we proceed to Week 1, Day 3-5, and so on.
